備註 Remarks





基本素養 Basic Literacy
□ 多元文化與國際視野。
 Multi -culture and global vision.
□ 倫理與人文素養
 Quality of humanism and ethics.
□ 永續環境與社會關懷
 Sustainable environment and care for society.
 

核心能力 Competence
□ 設計與執行實驗，以及數據分析與驗證理論的能力
 Design, experiment, analyze, interpret data, and verify theories.
■ 發掘、研判、診斷問題的能力
 Find, judge, examine problem.
□ 執行能源工程實務所需技術及工具之運用能力
 Technique for practicing engineering and using tools.
□ 誠信負責與務實素養
 Integrity and responsibility.
□ 認知能源時事議題，並培養持續學習的習慣與能力
 Understand latest news of energy and cultivate habits of keeping learning.
□ 運用數學、科學及工程知識以系統化方法解決能源工程問題的能力
 To train students to understand principles of mathematics, science and engineering, and use systematic methods to solve mechanical engineering.
□ 培養跨領域溝通及團隊合作的能力
 Cultivate cross-disciplinary communication and team work ability.
 

課程概述 Course Description
       潔淨化石燃料技術介紹Introduction to clean fossil fuel techniques    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
Learning new concepts and methods of clean fossil fuel technologiesPerforming experiments related to biomass enerbyTeam working with classmate to cope with energy problems 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Introduction / Review of Combustion: Diffusion Flames2Droplet Evaporation and Burning3Burning of Solids4Emission and Pollution5Biomass Gasification, Pyrolysis and Torrefaction6Biomass Characteristics7Fossil Fuel Combustion Technology - Exam8Invited Lecture I9Introduction to Tube Furnace and TGA10Tube Furnace Experiment11TGA Experiment12Invited Lecture II13CO2 Capture & Storage: Overview14CO2 Capture: Pre-Combustion15CO2 Capture: Post Combustion16CO2 Capture: Oxyfuel Combustion17CO2 Transportation & Storage18CO2 Capture & Storage - Exam 

